ENTRY            D0462   20260323   20260508   20260508       D151
SUBENT        D0462001   20260323   20260508   20260508       D151
BIB                  9         16
TITLE      Elastic scattering of 1.5-3.0 MeV deuterons by 12C,
            25Mg and 27A1
AUTHOR     (W.N.Wang, E.K.Lin, C.C.Hsu, T.Chiao, C.C.Chu)
INSTITUTE  (3CHFTHU)
REFERENCE  (J,CHP,5,1,1967)
FACILITY   (VDG,3CHFTHU) 3 MeV Van de Graaff
METHOD     (BCINT)
DETECTOR   (SIBAR) Two surface barrier detectors.
           (SOLST) Two solid state detectors were used to monitor
            the scattering deuterons
ERR-ANALYS The uncertainties in the absolute cross
            sections are believed to be within 15%, the probable
            error is due chiefly to the uncertainty in the
            normalization processes.
HISTORY    (20080327C)
           (20260323A) VT. Revision in the entry
ENDBIB              16
COMMON               1          3
EN-RSL
MEV
       0.05
ENDCOMMON            3
